  "detailed_description": "Welcome to Vertigo Battle Royale, Players parachute onto the last 4 floors of the building and fight to be the last one standing. The skyscraper is filled with weapons, ammo, and other items that players can use to gain an advantage. The play area shrinks vertically over time, forcing players closer together and increasing the tension. The winner is the last player or team standing at the end of the game.",
